HB 963 Original 2026 Regular Session Berault
Appropriates $150,000 out of the State General Fund (Direct) for FY 2025-2026 for payment
of the consent judgment against the state in the suit captioned Elva Moorhead, et al. v. Eagle,
Inc., et al., bearing No. 2022-02716, Division F, on the docket of the Civil District Court,
parish of Orleans.
Proposed law provides relative to payment. Provides relative to conflicts between judgment
and proposed law. Prohibits accrual of interest on the judgment as of the effective date of
proposed law.
Effective upon signature of the governor or lapse of time for gubernatorial action.
